  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "This range was selected to realistically represent the price of the most advanced iPhone model at the time of data collection ($1000; iPhone 14 Pro) as well as various other prices for older, used or discounted iPhones.",
    "In addition to the control variables used across Studies 1-2, we calculated the average effectiveness/WTP for each participant to further control for differences in averages on these ratings.",
    "We also included the position in which an ad was displayed to control for order effects.",
    "Similar to Studies 1 and 2, we measured participants' Big Five personality traits using the 30-item BFI-2-S 57.",
    "With Cronbach's alphas ranging from 0.81 to 0.89, the scale reliabilities were found to be good (Openness = 0.81, Conscientiousness = 0.89, Extraversion = 0.82, Agreeableness = 0.82 and Neuroticism = 0.86)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
